GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for new clients. These will be inserted into the target.
GROUP.NAME: ClientNew

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for Clients that no longer are in the source. The client will be deleted from the target.
GROUP.NAME: ClientMissing

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for when source and target data is exactly the same. These rows will not be processed. The DEFAULT group will be rows for existing clients that have changes. Those rows will be updated on target.
GROUP.EXPRESSION: ( NOT ISNULL(CLT_ID_CUR) ) AND ( NOT ISNULL(CLT_ID_NEW) ) AND ( RTRIM(MODEL_TYP_CD_CUR) = RTRIM(MODEL_TYP_CD_NEW) ) AND ( ( ISNULL(CLT_NM_CUR) AND ISNULL(CLT_NM_NEW) ) OR RTRIM(CLT_NM_CUR) = RTRIM(CLT_NM_NEW) ) AND ( ( ISNULL(CLIENT_CD_CUR) AND ISNULL(CLIENT_CD_NEW) ) OR RTRIM(CLIENT_CD_CUR) = RTRIM(CLIENT_CD_NEW) ) AND ( ( ISNULL(AP_COMPNY_CD_CUR) AND ISNULL(AP_COMPNY_CD_NEW) ) OR RTRIM(AP_COMPNY_CD_CUR) = RTRIM(AP_COMPNY_CD_NEW) AND ( ( ISNULL(BUS_SEG_CD_CUR) AND ISNULL(BUS_SEG_CD_NEW) ) OR RTRIM(BUS_SEG_CD_CUR) = RTRIM(BUS_SEG_CD_NEW) ) AND ( ( ISNULL(EFF_DT_CUR) AND ISNULL(EFF_DT_NEW) ) OR RTRIM(EFF_DT_CUR) = RTRIM(EFF_DT_NEW) ) AND ( ( ISNULL(END_DT_CUR) AND ISNULL(END_DT_NEW) ) OR RTRIM(END_DT_CUR) = RTRIM(END_DT_NEW) ) )
GROUP.NAME: ClientSame
